    "body": "## Summary\n\nFixes 22 standalone test failures introduced by #12357.\n\n`tensorrt_llm/_torch/auto_deploy/transform/library/rope.py` added a top-level\n`from ...custom_ops.attention.trtllm_attention import _TRTLLM_ROPE_INFO_KEY`,\nwhich transitively imports `tensorrt_llm.bindings.internal.thop` and\n`tensorrt_llm.functional`. In the standalone auto_deploy package those are\nunavailable, so `rope.py` itself fails to import — taking down every\nbackend-agnostic RoPE transform with it. As a result, 22 rope/qkv tests\nthat have nothing to do with TRT-LLM started failing in standalone mode.\n\nThe fix moves the TRT-LLM-specific code out into its own module so the\nstandalone import-guard mechanism can skip exactly the TRT-LLM-only piece:\n\n- `FuseRopeIntoTrtllmAttention` and its 7 helpers (`_FUSIBLE_ROPE_OPS`,\n  `_trace_to_rope`, `_extract_explicit_rope_info`, `_extract_complex_rope_info`,\n  `_convert_to_thop_cos_sin`, `_build_rope_info`, `_get_real_tensor`,\n  `_compute_cos_sin_from_inv_freq`, `_find_inv_freq_tensor`) →\n  new `transform/library/fuse_rope_into_trtllm_attention.py`. The new module\n  reuses `_trace_to_buffer_source` / `_get_nested_attr` / `_trace_back_index`\n  from `rope.py`. `library/__init__.py` already swallows `ImportError` /\n  `ModuleNotFoundError` for transform modules in standalone mode, so the new\n  file is silently skipped there.\n- The two TRT-LLM-only tests `test_fuse_qkv_with_trtllm_cache_insertion` /\n  `test_fuse_qkv_gqa_with_trtllm_cache_insertion` (and the `QKVAttentionModel`\n  they rely on for that pipeline) → new\n  `tests/.../transformations/library/test_gemm_fusion_trtllm.py`. The\n  remaining QKV/SwiGLU fusion tests stay in `test_gemm_fusion.py`.\n- `examples/auto_deploy/create_standalone_package.py`: add\n  `test_gemm_fusion_trtllm.py` to `EXCLUDE_TEST_FILES`.\n\nNo behavior change in the full TRT-LLM build — same transforms register, same\ntests run.\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [x] `pytest tests/unittest/auto_deploy/standalone` — 12/12 passed (was 11/12 with 22 sub-test failures)\n- [x] `pytest tests/unittest/auto_deploy/singlegpu/transformations/library/test_rope_transformation.py` — 20 passed, 2 xfailed\n- [x] `pytest tests/unittest/auto_deploy/singlegpu/transformations/library/test_gemm_fusion.py tests/unittest/auto_deploy/singlegpu/transformations/library/test_gemm_fusion_trtllm.py` — 26 passed, 8 skipped, 1 xfailed\n- [x] CI to verify AutoDeploy stages: `/bot run --extra-stage \"DGX_B200-4_GPUs-AutoDeploy-1, DGX_H100-4_GPUs-AutoDeploy-1\"`\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n## Release Notes\n\n* **Refactor**\n  * Reorganized RoPE fusion transformation into a dedicated module for improved code organization.\n\n* **Tests**\n  * Added comprehensive tests validating QKV GEMM fusion combined with TRT-LLM cached attention insertion for both dense and grouped query attention patterns.\n\n* **Chores**\n  * Updated standalone package generation to exclude specialized test files from distribution.\n\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
